    <td>What could have gone better in your learning?</td>
    <td></td>
  </tr>
  <tr>
    <td>I could have asked the person who designed the game about the purpose before playing. I also could have tried to get a better understanding of each game so I could have given a better evaluation of each game. I need to remember these tips for next time to improve my learning as well.</td>
    <td></td>
  </tr>
  <tr>
    <td>What changes do you need to make to improve your learning next time?</td>
    <td></td>
  </tr>
  <tr>
    <td>I need to keep going until the time is up and don’t get even a little bit distracted when working. I also need to keep my focus all the time instead of thinking about irrelevant things like what homework we got.</td>
